    "as_of": "2026-05-08",
    "source": "formula",
    "source_detail": "Self-test fixture closing the swaption_vol step coverage gap. Reuses the Phase-2 reference envelope catalog entry 07_swaption_vol_surface.json as the calibration plan. Three steps: (1) USD-OIS bootstrapped from 6 SOFR OIS quotes, (2) USD-SOFR-3M forward bootstrapped against the calibrated discount, (3) USD-SWAPTION-NORMAL-VOL SABR-fitted from 27 swaption-vol quotes (3 expiries \u00d7 3 tenors \u00d7 3 strikes; bilinear interpolation; normal-vol convention; \u03b2=0.0). The surface is produced as a vol_cube (not a vol_surface) \u2014 its presence in the calibrated market is the principal verification of the swaption_vol step. Expected outputs captured from Finstack's calibrate + black76 swaption-price round-trip; bit-stable reproduction is the contract.",
